Lionel Long https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lionel_Long 0 Lionel Joaquin Paul Long, OAM (1939 – 1 January 1998) was an Australian country and folk singer, songwriter, guitarist, actor and artist.Long became one of Australia's most successful and popular country and folk artists in the 1960s, releasing over a dozen albums for EMI. He was also well known for his acting appearances on television programs such as Homicide.
